{"tid":1666491,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"東京supreme","createTime":"2019-10-21T04:08:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T06:08:50.000Z","uid":13195,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6d9196063d4697ed6c033d8b43966318d5bda4f2","tid":1666491,"uid":13195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:08:17.000Z","msg":"十二月中會去東京，想問吓如果平時星期六就咁開舖去排會唔會買到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係要早一日星期五下晝去排隊抽籤？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係咪直接去代官山嗰間機會大啲？<br />\n<br />\n利申 無排過 淨係想問吓tee同hoodie"},{"pid":"bff5372b6da345ec30403f905fc14e44dbbee599","tid":1666491,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:13:27.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b8aa4982c940c62db7a1e454202fa6698016a9","tid":1666491,"uid":38772,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:25:06.000Z","msg":"著superme 算la"},{"pid":"37c8f0c37a44b2a8ac8906aac8adadd118c9c676","tid":1666491,"uid":96406,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:40:43.000Z","msg":"睇下果個week出啲咩<br />\n如果係勁野可能要早一日去排隊抽<br />\n如果普通野 星期六朝早7,8點去排喇"},{"pid":"c29d5b267cf820d1512e5cd5b3dc4fc13b6c5948","tid":1666491,"uid":13195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37c8f0c37a44b2a8ac8906aac8adadd118c9c676","tid":1666491,"uid":96406,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:40:43.000Z","msg":"睇下果個week出啲咩<br />\n如果係勁野可能要早一日去排隊抽<br />\n如果普通野 星期六朝早7,8點去排喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"好彩都住得算近 實凍撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90942b397d6b6e5435f83071e9efab7faecd0673","tid":1666491,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:29:53.000Z","msg":"[實用]    香城online防具升級詳細篇<br />\n<br />\n近呢一個月，我見到多左好多新入香城online嘅玩家，勇武/和理非都有好多工作做，鑑於有好多人唔知點配搭防具，眼見好多手足都只用貴價6092X，除左冇必要之外仲晒左好多錢，故此我係度再講一次點去配合適的防具。<br />\n<br />\n防毒面具：<br />\n中後/後防(物資站/噴漆師/文宣組/美化工程組/網上資訊組)<br />\n首選最合符經濟效益<br />\n包括單咀<br />\n3200/HF-52+3311K-55<br />\n一set最平100港幣有找<br />\n雙咀：<br />\n6200+6001/6003/6005(6005唔需要特登買，成本價貴)+5n11/5p71(唔建議5p71,如果要嘅不如買502再搭P100綿抵啲)+501蓋<br />\n例如：6200+6001CN+5n11+501 我見100已經有一set<br />\n而且 就算唔用5n11同501蓋 都ok 6001CN一對最平$30，我見$50通常都有<br />\n6003貴少少 $70成平價(睇你有冇運見到)<br />\n以上都可以頂到TG，但記得聞到味要即換<br />\n<br />\n想了解更多快啲入去連登睇啦😛<br />\n...<br />\n防毒面具篇完<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1666931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1666931</a>"},{"pid":"b6fb094c7c9c9f4a6307a177f9bea8f70ba641cd","tid":1666491,"uid":96406,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c29d5b267cf820d1512e5cd5b3dc4fc13b6c5948","tid":1666491,"uid":13195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"37c8f0c37a44b2a8ac8906aac8adadd118c9c676","tid":1666491,"uid":96406,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T07:40:43.000Z","msg":"睇下果個week出啲咩<br />\n如果係勁野可能要早一日去排隊抽<br />\n如果普通野 星期六朝早7,8點去排喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"好彩都住得算近 實凍撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T09:48:06.000Z","msg":"原宿排Supreme幾開心架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可以睇下啲人點著 同香港果啲好唔同 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n排完記得去食蛋包隻呀 超級推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1de3453fd194723b57fc54aaec70bbef5f4a62e2","tid":166649